  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to describe the evolution of pulmonary function in 3 neuromuscular diseases :
      Duchenne muscular dystrophy, Werdnig-Hoffinann disease, congenital myopathy, monitored in
      Besançon university hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
